  "notes": "## Zahlungsabgleich (Payment Auto-Matching)\n\n### Fixes Applied (v2)\n- Changed tableId 'invoices' -> 'rechnungen' (actual schema table)\n- Changed column 'total' -> 'brutto' (actual rechnungen column)\n- Changed status filter 'sent,action_required_dunning' -> 'offen' (valid CHECK constraint values)\n- Changed UPDATE status 'paid' -> 'bezahlt' (valid CHECK constraint value: offen/bezahlt/storniert)\n- Changed column 'paid_date' -> 'paid_at' (actual rechnungen column)\n- Removed non-existent columns: payment_transaction_id, payment_amount_received, payment_matched_by (store in metadata)\n- Replaced jobs_queue with automation_log (action, target, metadata)\n- Transaction match data stored in automation_log.metadata JSONB\n\n### Setup Required\n1. **GoCardless**: Register at bankaccountdata.gocardless.com. Obtain access token and account ID.\n2. **Env Vars**: Set GOCARDLESS_ACCESS_TOKEN and GOCARDLESS_ACCOUNT_ID in n8n.\n3. **Supabase rechnungen table**: Uses columns: status (offen/bezahlt/storniert), brutto, paid_at, kunde_name.\n\n### Matching Strategies (dual)\n1. **Amount match**: Rechnung brutto within ±0.01 EUR of transaction amount with status=offen\n2. **Reference match**: Rechnung leistungsart found in transaction remittance information\n\n### Scheduling\n- Runs at 07:00 daily (1 hour before dunning check at 08:00)\n- Processes last 7 days of transactions to catch delayed bookings\n\n### Manual Review\n- Unmatched transactions logged in automation_log with action='payment_unmatched' and requires_manual_review=true in metadata"
}
